they get such good medicine?

593
00:56:01,257 --> 00:56:03,350
Ain't that right, Yanker?

594
00:56:03,426 --> 00:56:06,054
You tell them, Yanker, eh?

595
00:56:06,129 --> 00:56:08,620
Ha!

596
00:56:08,698 --> 00:56:12,566
